    "causal_summary": "The stress test cycle format has been authored ad-hoc three times now (v1.0.1, v1.0.2, v1.0.3). The shape that emerged is reusable: 30-cell scoring matrix (4 dimensions x packets), 0-2 rubric per dimension, findings narrative plus `findings-rubric.json` machine-readable sidecar, PROVEN/NEUTRAL/REGRESSION verdict ladder, weighted aggregate percentage. **None of it is documented in sk-doc**, so the next cycle (v1.0.4 or a different domain) starts from zero.",
